          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#10003;</span><strong>Dashboard Help page</strong> — MCP-first guidance, 8-tool installer, agent prompt examples, curated CLI reference, 12-tool MCP reference</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5 shrink-0">&#10003;</span><strong>Admin org endpoints</strong> — GET/POST /api/v1/admin/orgs + PUT /api/v1/admin/orgs/:id/tier for internal provisioning</li>
